DI PC SNORT

install snort

setting di snort.conf:
HOME_NET 192.168.24.0/28
EXTERNAL_NET any

sudo apt install rsyslog -y

tambahkan output syslog di snort.conf

sudo nano /etc/snort/snort.conf
ctrl + w output alert (step 6)
enabled output alert_syslog: LOG_AUTH LOG_ALERT (hilangkan "#")
ctrl + o
ctrl + x

lalu buka

sudo nano /etc/rsyslog.conf
scroll paling bawah dan tambahkan *.* @192.168.24.2:514 (IP masing-masing ya. portnya harus 514)
ctrl + o
ctrl + x
sudo systemctl restart rsyslog



DI PC FLOODLIGHT CONTROLLER

sudo nano /etc/rsyslog.conf

hapus "#" di :
module(load="imudp")
input(type="imudp" port="514")

ctrl + o
ctrl + x

sudo systemctl restart rsyslog



Kembali ke PC SNORT

nc -zv -u 192.168.24.2 514

jika succeded maka jos

pantau log yang dikirimkan oleh snort ke controller:
tail -f /var/log/auth.log
tail -f /var/log/syslog
